Dear friends, how about transforming the process of legislation by a [[unpartei/VersionControlSystem|VersionControlSystem]][[http://google.com/search?q=VersionControlSystem|º]] like [[unpartei/GIT|GIT]][[http://google.com/search?q=GIT|º]], where everybody has read and write access and where each amendment is accessable via a [[unpartei/DifferenceEngine|DifferenceEngine]][[http://google.com/search?q=DifferenceEngine|º]]?
